#. module: sale_lazada
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale_lazada.field_lazada_order_item__status
msgid ""
"The status of the order item on Lazada:\n"
"- Draft: The order item is in draft status by default.\n"
"- Confirmed: The order item has been packed.\n"
"- Processing: The order item is ready to ship.\n"
"- Delivered: The order item has been shipped or delivered.\n"
"- Canceled: The order item has been canceled.\n"
"- Manual: The order item has to be processed manually on Lazada."
msgstr ""
"The status of the order item on Lazada:\n"
"- Draft: The order item is in draft status by default.\n"
"- Confirmed: The order item has been packed.\n"
"- Processing: The order item is ready to ship.\n"
"- Delivered: The order item has been shipped or delivered.\n"
"- Canceled: The order item has been canceled.\n"
"- Manual: The order item has to be processed manually on Lazada."

#. module: sale_lazada
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale_lazada.field_lazada_shop__fbl_location_id
msgid ""
"The stock location representing inventory managed by Lazada under the FBL "
"(Fulfilled by Lazada) program. This location is automatically created when "
"you set up the shop. Stock moves to this location represent items sent to "
"Lazada warehouses for fulfillment."
msgstr ""
"The stock location representing inventory managed by Lazada under the FBL "
"(Fulfilled by Lazada) program. This location is automatically created when "
"you set up the shop. Stock moves to this location represent items sent to "
"Lazada warehouses for fulfillment."

#. module: sale_lazada
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale_lazada/models/lazada_order_item.py:0
msgid ""
"The stock move must be related to the same sale order line as the Lazada "
"order item."
msgstr "يجب أن تكون حركة المخزون مرتبطة بنفس بند أمر البيع مثل عنصر طلب Lazada."

#. module: sale_lazada
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale_lazada.field_lazada_item__lazada_item_extern_id
msgid ""
"The unique identifier for an item in Lazada. An item in Lazada is equivalent"
" to a product variant in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"The unique identifier for an item in Lazada. An item in Lazada is equivalent "
"to a product variant in Odoo."

#. module: sale_lazada
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale_lazada.field_lazada_shop__fbm_warehouse_id
msgid ""
"The warehouse containing inventory that will be synchronized to Lazada for "
"FBM (Fulfilled by Merchant) orders. Select the warehouse where you store "
"products that you ship directly to customers. If not set, your company's "
"default warehouse will be used."
msgstr ""
"The warehouse containing inventory that will be synchronized to Lazada for "
"FBM (Fulfilled by Merchant) orders. Select the warehouse where you store "
"products that you ship directly to customers. If not set, your company's "
"default warehouse will be used."

#. module: sale_lazada
#: model:ir.model.constraint,message:sale_lazada.constraint_sale_order_unique_lazada_order_ref_lazada_shop_id
